==English==

===Etymology===
[[w:Karl Marx|Karl Marx]] + [[-ism]].

===Noun===
'''Marxism''' (''uncountable'')

# The [[socialist]] philosophy of Karl Marx.
# The [[socialist]] ideology of the folowers of Karl Marx; a radical, revolutionary political philosophy that aims to capture state power, introduce a [[dictatorship of the proletariat]], and then progress to [[anarchy]].

